Package edu.lehigh.cse216.rdm325.backend

Class SimpleRequestUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.lehigh.cse216.rdm325.backend.SimpleRequestUser
  • public class SimpleRequestUser
extends java.lang.Object
    SimpleRequestUser provides a format for clients to present User info strings to the server. NB: since this will be created from JSON, all fields must be public, and we do not need a constructor.
